name: membrane_6inputs_EFFN
model:
EnhancedSpatioTemporalFFN2(
  (mlp): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=200, out_features=200, bias=True)
    (1): SiLU()
    (2): Linear(in_features=200, out_features=200, bias=True)
    (3): SiLU()
  )
  (final): Linear(in_features=400, out_features=1, bias=True)
)
optimizer:
Adam (
Parameter Group 0
    amsgrad: False
    betas: (0.9, 0.999)
    capturable: False
    differentiable: False
    eps: 1e-08
    foreach: None
    fused: None
    initial_lr: 0.001
    lr: 0.001
    maximize: False
    weight_decay: 0
)
